# Admin Web App Guidelines

- **Tech Stack**: React 18, Vite, TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui components
- **Validation**: Zod schemas for all forms & API payloads
- **Animations**: Framer Motion for page transitions and micro-interactions
- **Internationalization**: i18n setup with en·es·ar, runtime locale switching
- **Accessibility**: WCAG-AA compliance (semantic HTML, ARIA roles, focus management)
- **PWA**: Service worker, install prompt, offline caching of assets
- **Routing**: Define routes under `/login`, `/dashboard`, `/projects`, etc.
- **Map Components**: Use a shared `<MapCard>` that renders PostGIS-powered markers
